# Package manager: Bun

- Install and resolve packages with **`bun install`**, not npm/yarn/pnpm.
- Run scripts with **`bun run …`**, workspace targets with **`bun --filter @scope/pkg …`**.
- Run one-off CLIs with **`bunx …`** instead of **`npx …`** when possible.
- To check a package on the registry, prefer **`bun info <pkg>`** over npm view.

The root `package.json` pins Bun via `packageManager`.
